SYNOPSIS

     use File::Digest qw(digest_files);
    
     my $res = digest_files(
         files => ["file1", "file2"],
         algorithm => 'md5', # default md5, available also: crc32, sha1, sha256
     );

DESCRIPTION

SEE ALSO

    sum from PerlPowerTools (which only supports older algorithms like
    CRC32).

    Backend modules: Digest::CRC, Digest::MD5, Digest::SHA.

    xsum from App::xsum which can also check checksums/digests from
    checksum file e.g. MD5SUMS.

